{
  "stem": "4570.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one said to the other, they are even worse off because they are not Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They will suffer even longer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because we had no, no stars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We only had that we are from the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so I said, oh, well, that's not very good news.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we marched and marched.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's very-- quite a bit to go to, to the camp, uphill through the woods.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought, oh, should I run away?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shouldn't I?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have the guts to run away, and I think the chances would have been pretty slim.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we came to this-- it looked like some Mickey Mouse castle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Quite-- everything was so unreal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It looked like a castle that has a drawbridge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still don't know if it-- it's a drawbridge or, or-- it, it had a bridge-- first of all some, some buildings, and then there was a big bridge, and then you went to the rest of the-- of the camp.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came there and, again, the boss.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So clean.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything has to be nice and-- so they took us again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took away our, our clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I still had the photo and I did something very silly with the [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Buddha. ?] I put it down here and it fell out and went down the drain.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the last-- so just before the war I lost the [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Buddha. ?] And I kept the photo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am under the impression that they didn't have clothes for women because they thought we are coming there, we are going in the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't prepare for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But because the trains were not going, they didn't get the poisonous gas.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
